'''加茂语'''是一种[[壮侗语系|壮侗语系]]语言，或是[[孤立语言|孤立语言]]，分布在中国[[海南岛|海南岛]]南部。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Miyake |first1=Marc |author-link1=Marc Miyake |title=11.9.20.22:04: Is Jiamao Hlai? |url=http://www.amritas.com/110924.htm#09202204 |website=www.amritas.com |date=September 20, 2011 |access-date=2021-06-13 |archive-date=2019-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190804112844/http://www.amritas.com/110924.htm#09202204 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Norquest|first=Peter|title=A Phonological Reconstruction of Proto-Hlai|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=d6i8CgAAQBAJ|year=2015|publisher=BRILL|isbn=978-90-04-30052-1|access-date=2021-06-13|archive-date=2021-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210620141306/https://books.google.com/books?id=d6i8CgAAQBAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>加茂语使用者的[[外名与内名|自称]]是{{IPA|tʰai}}<sup>1</sup>。<ref name=tone>声调符号参见[[原始台语#声调|原始台语#声调]]。</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=刘 |first1=援朝 |title=黎语加茂话概况 |journal=民族語文 |date=2008 |volume=5}}</ref>

==系属分类==
加茂语长期以来都被认为属于[[壮侗语系|壮侗语系]][[黎语支|黎语支]]，但它的词汇与黎语相差过大，Graham Thurgood (1992)认为它可能有[[南亚语系|南亚语系]]底层。Norquest (2007)识别出不少不包含于[[原始黎语|原始黎语]]的加茂语词汇，这更能说明加茂语不属于黎语支。<ref name="Norquest2015">{{cite book|last=Norquest|first=Peter|title=A Phonological Reconstruction of Proto-Hlai|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=d6i8CgAAQBAJ|year=2015|publisher=BRILL|isbn=978-90-04-30052-1|page=3|access-date=2021-06-13|archive-date=2021-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210620141306/https://books.google.com/books?id=d6i8CgAAQBAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref> Hsiu (2018)<ref>Hsiu, Andrew. 2018. [https://sites.google.com/site/msealangs/home/blog/jiamao The origins of Jiamao] {{Wayback|url=https://sites.google.com/site/msealangs/home/blog/jiamao |date=20201009124542 }}.</ref>注意到加茂语包含不少来自一种现已灭绝的[[藏缅语族|藏缅语族]]语言的借词。

==使用人口==
1980年代，加茂语使用人口约有5万人，分布在海南岛中部和中南部，主要在[[保亭黎族苗族自治县|保亭黎族苗族自治县]]加茂镇。它和黎语支语言共享的词汇不到一半。<ref name="norquest">Norquest, Peter K. 2007. [http://gradworks.umi.com/32/84/3284367.html ''A Phonological Reconstruction of Proto-Hlai''] {{Wayback|url=http://gradworks.umi.com/32/84/3284367.html |date=20160303210532 }}. Ph.D. Department of Anthropology, University of Arizona.</ref>

加茂语分布在[[陵水黎族自治县|陵水黎族自治县]]本号、南平、文罗、祖关、隆广和田仔等村。<ref>郎啊朗. 2006. [http://bbs.tianya.cn/post-360-1314-1.shtml“ 保亭加茂黎族”是真的黎族吗？]</ref>在陵水县，加茂语被称为“台”“塞”或“加我”。{{cn|date=December 2020}}加茂语还分布在[[琼中黎族苗族自治县|琼中黎族苗族自治县]]中平镇和乘坡农场的30个村。<ref>董亚岭. 2013. [http://lizu.baike.com/article-1103157.html 想了解琼中县的语言和方言分布吗] {{Wayback|url=http://lizu.baike.com/article-1103157.html |date=20180612142055 }}.</ref>

加茂语有4种方言，<ref name="baike">辛世彪. 2013. {{cite web|url=http://lizu.baike.com/article-1004623.html|title=《加茂黎语的四大方言》一文看过吗 - 黎族百科|website=lizu.baike.com|access-date=2017-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171010054600/http://lizu.baike.com/article-1004623.html|archive-date=2017-10-10|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref name="sina">辛世彪. 2009. {{cite web|url=http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_49d8b2980100c9nf.html|website=blog.sina.com.cn|title=加茂黎语的四大方言_辛世彪_新浪博客|access-date=2017-12-30|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303222722/http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_49d8b2980100c9nf.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>分别是加茂、六弓、田仔和群英。{{cn|date=December 2020}}

